---

### [choco://virtio-win](choco://virtio-win/s=https://nuts.bcurran3.org/nuget/chocolatey/)
To use choco:// protocol URLs, install [choco:// Protocol support ](https://nuts.bcurran3.org/feeds/chocolatey/choco-protocol-support/versions)

---

KVM/QEMU Windows guest drivers, for both paravirtual and emulated hardware.
    

